@startuml
title Planning Scenario 'default operator information' - V1.0.0

hide footbox
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantPadding 40
  BoxPadding 10
  LifeLineBorderColor #777777
  LifeLineBorderThickness 1
  LifeLineBackgroundColor transparent
  MessageAlign left
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFDD
  BorderColor #777777
}

participant "MP" as MP
participant "Lookup" as Lookup
participant "TO" as TO

note over TO
<b>ProcessIdentifiers:</b> DEFAULT
end note

note over MP,Lookup
Endpoints that could be used by the MP:
/operator/meta
/operator/available-assets
/operator/stations
/operator/regions
/operator/operating-calendar
/operator/operating-hours
/operator/pricing-plans
/operator/information
end note

MP -> TO : e.g. /operator/available-assets
activate TO
TO --> MP : available assettypes (optionally containing assets)
deactivate TO

note over MP,Lookup
Endpoints that could be used by the MP:
/operator/meta
/operator/information
/operator/regions
end note

Lookup -> TO : e.g. /operator/meta
activate TO
TO --> Lookup : precise description of the implementation of the API
deactivate TO

@enduml